Package: hmmTradeR
Type: Package
Title: hmm models tools for trading
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Serge", "Moisan",
      email = "serge.moisan@yahoo.fr",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package proposes different tools,
    written in C++ (for speed)and R to test different parameters 
    for hmm model of stock prices. It generates signals for backtesting and
    evaluation of the different models.
